OL,3,C'It is crystal clear that he is
OL,4,Cunfit': Lockerbie man avoids murder
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FA Lockerbie man accused of murdering
OL,8,Fhis wife, who disappeared in 1984,
OL,9,Fwill not stand trial after being
OL,10,Fdeemed mentally unfit.
OL,12,FWilliam Hodge, 79, is alleged to have
OL,13,Fkilled the 34-year-old Marion Hodge in
OL,14,FLockerbie, Dumfries and Galloway.
OL,16,FThough she was declared legally dead
OL,17,Fby the Court of Session in Edinburgh
OL,18,Fin 1992, the body of the mother-of-two
OL,19,Fhas never been found.
