OL,3,C'It is crystal clear that he is
OL,4,Cunfit': Lockerbie man avoids murder
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FIn terms of a trial, Professor
OL,8,FMcPherson stated that Hodge would
OL,9,F"struggle" to instruct a lawyer and
OL,10,Funderstand the trial process.
OL,12,FThe professor, however, did say that
OL,13,FHodge was able to understand the
OL,14,Fpenalties that would be imposed.
OL,16,FThere was an investigation into the
OL,17,Fdeath in 1984 and a reinvestigation in
OL,18,F2006 when there was no further action
OL,19,Ftaken.
