OL,3,C'It is crystal clear that he is
OL,4,Cunfit': Lockerbie man avoids murder
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FThe matter was then looked at again in
OL,8,F2021, and this has resulted in the
OL,9,Fcurrent prosecution.
OL,11,FJudge Lord Mulholland fixed an
OL,12,Fexamination of facts, which is
OL,13,Fexpected to last four weeks at the
OL,14,FHigh Court in Glasgow in September.
OL,16,FThe judge said: "It is crystal clear
OL,17,Fthat he is unfit ` in all the
OL,18,Fcircumstances, I uphold the unfitness
OL,19,Fto plead motion."
